text: If got ZERO star rating I'll gladly give them ZERO star. Staff attitude is super bad. Walked in to buy candies for gifts but was shoo-ed away by them saying they don't sell things in the morning. Asked me to go back at 1pm to buy. Never going back again!

The first time going this place to buy food.. And guess what i found.. Last week my friend bought the Big Bang Seaweed Tom Yum @ $17.12 after gst.. which is only the 23 April 2014. And today my another friend went to buy the Original Seaweed @ $21+ .. And we went back to asked.. the person in a rude manner said that they increase the price.. Over just a week , it increase $4.00.. are you kidding me.. and the staff there all damn rude.. no manner..
Good service with variety of choices
